    "attributes": {
        "action": "Electric installation licence system & ban sale of materials to the unlicensed",
        "additional_details": "We hope this policy will stop unqualified individuals buying and installing 240 volt and above electrical materials, which could pose a serious risk to life by electrocution or fire.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to introduce a licencing system for purchasing electrical installation materials, and to ban the sale of electrical installation materials, distribution boards, etc that are 240 volts and above to unlicensed companies or individuals.",
